name: Tezpunks
description:
Tezpunks

Year AD 7702, a group of punks are assigned a mysterious mission. These punks are very deadly. They have their own superpowers. Objectives of the mission will be communicated to them from the command center. For now, the only objective communicated to the punks is to time travel to 2021. 

ID #005
Male


Name         : Balkis 
Strength     : 100/100
Intelligence : 92/100


Travels from planet to planet collecting information, skills, weapons, slaves. 
His role in earth mission 2021 is a secret. 
According to legends, if Balkis stays in a place for long, something serious is about to happen there.
